snippet.title: Crab Island Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Crab Island is a relaxing fishing game where you collect dancing crabs. "Grow your island, take care of your crabs, dress them up, and summon Crabthulhu!" I have absolutely no idea what to expect from this upcoming mobile game, but I'm excited to try it 🦀 https://apps.apple.com/app/crab-island/id1607881993 #ios #indiegames #mobilegames
